name: mysterious heroine x alter | All ascensions outfits (fate) MHXA
description:
v1.1
Full remake of LORA with new images and new tagging method

Main tag is MHXA
Lora weight >0.7. I recommend 0.8

  • First ascension: MHXA, plaid scarf, coat, school outfit. I also included classical outfit tag alongside dataset but it don't work well, you can try it

  • Second: MHXA, white shirt, black shorts, (sport outfit), jacket. Jacket is optional

  • Third(vader): MHXA, vader outfit. Armor/breastplate are optional

  • Idol: MHXA, idol outfit. Most unstable one but works well. Guitar is in training data but cant confirm that always be right one.

-----v1------------------------------
My first attempt to make LORA.
Control tag for this is MHXA. Tested on AOM3ab1 and Anythingv5PrtRE
Recommended power of LORA is 0.8
To invoke her second ascension outfit use MHXA, jacket, bike shorts
For first one use MHXA, red scarf, coat
Blond hair tag might be included if you get different hair color. I didn't include it in samples
Please share your images. And let me know if you want other ascension included.I am planning to add Idol version if i have time
